message.content:
1. A standard diameter needle was used to collect oocytes.
2. A total of 215 oocytes were collected with the standard diameter needle.
3. The standard diameter needle was used to aspirate 355 follicles.
4. The collection rate with the standard diameter needle was 60.6%.
5. A thinner needle was also used to collect oocytes.
6. A total of 203 oocytes were collected with the thinner needle.
7. The thinner needle was used to aspirate 352 follicles.
8. The collection rate with the thinner needle was 57.7%.
9. The p-value comparing the two collection rates was 0.23.

messages.content:
Statement: The standard diameter needle was used to collect a total of 215 oocytes from 355 aspirated follicles (60.6%) compared to 203 oocytes from 352 aspirated follicles (57.7%) with the thinner needle (p = 0.23).
